1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with indoor localization using WiFi signals, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper proposes a phase retrieval scheme to estimate the channel impulse response, which involves the use of information theory concepts. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper may involve the use of machine learning techniques for localization. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper may involve the use of control systems for localization. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with signal processing of WiFi signals, which may fall under the domain of multimedia.
